The paper deals with data augmentation for neural network training, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a new algorithm for generating nonstationary augmentation policy schedules, which involves optimization and search techniques that are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and deep learning (cs.DL).
